        <Meaning id="e88b2e61-ac61-419e-a5f0-13dbcc585f21" type="Noun">
          <Vi>Cá hồi</Vi>
          <En>A large, silvery fish that lives in the sea but migrates up freshwater rivers to spawn; also the pinkish-orange flesh of this fish, commonly eaten.</En>
          <Example>We grilled fresh salmon with lemon and dill for dinner.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="72da6cea-a95d-442e-8632-0bf9a1202e40">
